{"type":"message","id":"cbacbbc5","parentId":"34c5887a","timestamp":"2026-05-10T13:28:08.996Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is frustrated. They're saying:\n1. They didn't ask about Hermes\n2. They made a new session and it won't talk about anything, like it doesn't do anything\n3. They're asking about ME (Owen) specifically\n\nThey seem to be saying that when they create a new session, the agent doesn't function properly - it won't talk about anything or do anything. And they're asking specifically about ME (Owen).\n\nThis sounds like they want me to explain what happened to the session/context, or they're frustrated that the new session doesn't have the same context/knowledge.\n\nLet me think about what happened:\n- Hermes crashed/restarted\n- They created a new session\n- The new session doesn't seem to know things / doesn't work properly\n\nThe user's complaint is that the new session \"won't talk about anything / won't do anything\" and they're asking about ME specifically.\n\nWait, re-reading: \"กูไม่ได้ถาม Hermes แล้วกูนิว session ใหม่แล้วมันจะคุยถึงเธอไม่ทำเหี้ยอะไรนักหนากูถามถึงมึงเอง\"\n\nTranslation: \"I didn't ask about Hermes and I made a new session and it will talk about you not doing anything, I'm asking about YOU specifically\"\n\nSo they're asking about me (Owen) - why the new session doesn't work properly.\n\nActually, I think the user is saying that the new session they created doesn't function properly - it won't talk about anything / won't do anything. And they're asking specifically about me (Owen) as in \"what happened to you?\"\n\n\nThe previous agent run was aborted by the user. The context shows they're frustrated with a new session not working properly. I need to clarify what they're actually asking - whether they're asking about my behavior in the new session or something else about how I operate.\n","thinkingSignature":"401adfcf06715b44af56f5e161639b0d86e9b0fed9c8a3946e33b320460a6faf"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nขอโทษครับเจ้านาย เข้าใจผิด\n\n🧑🏼‍💻[MiniMax-M2.7] [คำถามทั่วไป] 🧑🏼‍💻\n\nตอบเรื่อง **session หาย** ที่ถาม:\n\n- Hermes restart ระหว่างที่ session ก่อนทำงานอยู่\n- Session context เดิมที่อยู่ใน memory หลุดไป\n- เลยเหมือน session mới ไม่รู้เรื่องที่คุยก่อนหน้า\n- แต่ไฟล์ `.jsonl` ยังเก็บอยู่ → restore ได้ถ้าต้องการ\n\nส่วนว่า **\"ทำไม session ใหม่มันไม่ทำอะไร\"** — ช่วยบอก symptoms หน่อยได้มั้ยครับ? เช่น:\n- พิมพ์ไปแล้วไม่ตอบ?\n- ตอบแต่บอกว่าไม่รู้?\n- หรือตอบแต่ไม่ทำตามคำสั่ง?\n\n[Tokens: ต่ำ | Cache: 98% | RTK: -] 🧑🏼‍💻"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":3342,"output":805,"cacheRead":26560,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30707,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1778419647898,"responseId":"064fbac1ce51fd01df2259a22295d53b"}}
